    "severity": "Sev-1 (Critical)",
    "description": "Unexpected Long Running Job incident on the Finance pipeline (RTL_FIN_ULRJ): finance GL trial balance close job duration anomaly.",
    "symptoms": "Monthly close DAG jumped from 1h50m to 5h20m this cycle.",
    "root_cause": "A new intercompany elimination rule set was deployed in SAP FI/CO mid-month, causing the SQL join in the elimination step to become non-sargable (function wrapped on indexed column).",
    "business_impact": "Delayed month-end close reporting to Finance leadership by half a business day.",
    "resolution": "Rewrite elimination query predicate to keep the indexed column bare; add query plan regression testing to the finance dbt CI pipeline."
  },
